<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">首合尾5法，是指首数相加时10，尾数都是5的两个两位数相乘时，可将首数之积加上525，，即得所求之积。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">100ab+525</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a、b分别表示被乘数与乘数十位上的数字。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">25×85=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 25×85</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100×2×8+525</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100×16+525</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1600+525</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2125</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>